<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - (ạ̹frḥ yạ ạbny wblạsẖ dmwʿ .. ʿysẖ ạ̉yạmk wyạ yswʿ
 syb ạlmsẖạkl klhạ ʿlyh .. wdwq ạlfrḥẗ mn ạ̹ydyh)2
 1- (ạ̹rmy ʿlyh kl hmwmk .. whw ydbr qwt ywmk
 ạ̹wʿy̱ fy ywm tbạt ḥzyn .. dh hw ʿsẖạnk wfy̱ ạldyn)2
 2- (ạ̹frḥ lạ̉nk msẖ wḥyd .. dh yswʿ fy ạldnyạ lyk snyd
 lw fạkr ạ̹nh ʿnk bʿyd .. tbqy̱ gẖlṭạn gẖlṭạn ạ̉kyd)2
 3- (lmạ tfrḥ ṭfl ṣgẖyr .. trsm ʿly̱ wsẖh ḍḥkẗ tḥyr
 sạʿthạ htnsy̱ kl ậlạmk .. htsẖwf ạlfrḥẗ ṭwl ạ̉yạmk)2</lyrics>
<title>ạ̹frḥ</title>
</song>